Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.01,0:00:04.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,0)}{\fs40}羅蘭德王宮
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.63,0:00:04.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盧納帝國和加斯塔克…？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.34,0:00:06.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.00,0:00:08.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可屬實
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.20,0:00:12.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然並未公開聲明和加斯塔克聯手
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.33,0:00:15.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而勾結斯提亞里德公爵等人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.28,0:00:17.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,企圖暗殺陛下的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.21,0:00:19.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毫無疑問是盧納王
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.66,0:00:22.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.18,0:00:27.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盧納王說表面上還是想和我國保持友好關係嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.48,0:00:31.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 屬下未能面見國王
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.40,0:00:34.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他似乎躲在盧納國內的小堡壘內
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.09,0:00:37.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受到了加斯塔克使者的威脅
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.13,0:00:40.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連國王都不得不屈服的威脅嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.85,0:00:42.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多少人被殺了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.79,0:00:45.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,據說守衛堡壘的所有士兵都被殺了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.86,0:00:50.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,問題還在後頭
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.49,0:00:51.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根據情報
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.72,0:00:54.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傳聞加斯塔克在同史特歐爾帝國的戰鬥中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.28,0:00:57.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使用了奇異的魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.65,0:00:58.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇異的魔法？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.05,0:01:01.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說那魔法只用一發
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.75,0:01:04.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就抵消了史特歐爾的大規模攻擊魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.42,0:01:07.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還將當場的軍隊全數消滅
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.67,0:01:10.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一時間讓人難以置信
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.14,0:01:13.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但若這是事實
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.94,0:01:17.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加斯塔克使者能使盧納帝國屈服的事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.99,0:01:19.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該也未必是謊言
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.44,0:01:25.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加斯塔克也開始使用了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.64,0:01:27.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇者遺物
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.93,0:01:31.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果事態發展到各國一齊開始收集遺物
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.55,0:01:34.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彼此互相攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.47,0:01:37.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到時候 世界就…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.15,0:02:06.17,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}追憶の扉を見上げて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.68,0:02:12.04,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}聞いていた音は囁き
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.47,0:02:17.90,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}導いて魂の輪廻
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.16,0:02:23.48,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}一片の光の道へ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.71,0:02:27.81,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}貫く痛みはInnocentre
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.00,0:02:32.15,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}信じたいよ 孤独じゃないこと
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.82,0:02:37.82,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}ここは彷徨いParadise
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.90,0:02:43.60,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}白く心染める翼で
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.86,0:02:50.48,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}もし君の瞳に 辿り着けたら
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.62,0:02:54.05,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}笑って 抱きしめて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.47,0:02:59.87,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}生まれてきた意味を知れ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.04,0:03:03.43,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}見つめ合って 始まるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.82,0:03:07.44,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}Destiny in a jail
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.93,0:03:11.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.80,0:03:12.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.27,0:03:16.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,席恩那傢伙 不知道現在在幹嘛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.95,0:03:22.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,600)}{\fs40}Kill the King
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.86,0:03:19.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正肯定還是老樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.38,0:03:22.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十惡不赦地耍些卑劣手段吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.86,0:03:25.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是啊 都怪那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.74,0:03:26.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要下手嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.58,0:03:28.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 等著瞧席恩
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.84,0:03:29.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等我回了羅蘭德
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.04,0:03:32.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要把你虐虐虐虐死啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.28,0:03:36.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.60,0:03:39.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們為啥會落到這步田地啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.85,0:03:42.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是因為你一如既往
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.00,0:03:45.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非禮我們所乘船隻上的女乘客
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.23,0:03:47.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,觸了船員們的逆鱗…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.82,0:03:48.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,觸你個頭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.16,0:03:50.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且我看到的事實是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.57,0:03:52.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為你和蜜爾可他們大打出手
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.90,0:03:54.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,船才翻了個底朝天
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.83,0:04:08.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還以為那幫人帶阿爾亞他們回了羅蘭德能清靜點
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.89,0:04:11.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果居然那麼快就回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.37,0:04:13.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 反正他們應該也不會有事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.15,0:04:16.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 真的假的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.27,0:04:19.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 看來是暴風雨
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.54,0:04:21.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還說得這麼悠閒
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.55,0:04:38.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 我要死了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.15,0:04:52.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還活著
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.81,0:04:55.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,強啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.45,0:04:58.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還以為剛才死定了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.78,0:05:02.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲莉絲？喂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.95,0:05:08.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像在烤什麼的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.64,0:05:15.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉 蜜爾可隊長
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.13,0:05:18.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有我盧克·斯塔卡德跟著
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.49,0:05:21.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隊員還被沖得七零八落
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.56,0:05:24.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天一天亮我立刻去找你們
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.84,0:05:26.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在此之前請一定要平安無事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.93,0:05:29.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.38,0:05:33.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無意識中做了全隊的份
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.64,0:05:37.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蜜爾可隊長最喜歡這種野營的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.85,0:05:40.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉 她現在到底在哪兒呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.20,0:05:53.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼怎麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.87,0:05:55.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然進入戰鬥狀態啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.41,0:06:03.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美味
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.88,0:06:06.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,調味很好還去了腥味
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.36,0:06:08.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種準備周到的類型…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.30,0:06:22.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萊納·琉特
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.82,0:06:25.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是…破忌者部隊的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.94,0:06:33.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盧克他們沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.36,0:06:34.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有萊納
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.95,0:06:36.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萊納…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.66,0:06:37.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.97,0:06:40.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,握緊我的手絕對別放開
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.80,0:06:44.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定…會救你的 萊納
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.21,0:06:55.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個人？這麼說現在的話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.02,0:06:57.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等著我 萊納
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.24,0:07:07.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.07,0:07:08.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼 還以為是誰呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.34,0:07:10.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來是被萊納始亂終棄的女人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.08,0:07:16.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 我才沒被拋棄呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.04,0:07:19.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒是你 快給我放了萊納
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.59,0:07:23.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道你用強制手段操縱著萊納
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.58,0:07:24.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是誤會
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.18,0:07:28.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是被他威脅 情非得已
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.49,0:07:30.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萊納才不可能做那種事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.79,0:07:33.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也希望這不是事實
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.39,0:07:36.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他不光對我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.65,0:07:39.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚至還對我妹妹下手
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.47,0:07:44.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每天晚上都…後面我實在說不出口
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.20,0:07:48.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對不對不對
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.40,0:07:50.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萊納才不是那種人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.92,0:07:54.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前幾天委託你們照顧了兩個孩子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.79,0:07:57.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實他們是那男人的私生子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.40,0:07:58.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.43,0:08:01.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,證據就是 他們非常敬愛萊納
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.87,0:08:03.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一看就很熟對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.19,0:08:05.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不僅如此
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.85,0:08:08.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他在奈爾法還接連對皇都的人妻下手
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.09,0:08:12.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在盧納不斷誘拐過路村姑
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.88,0:08:14.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚至連她們的母親都不放過
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.01,0:08:18.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.51,0:08:20.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼我連你的份也要做
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.44,0:08:23.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也真夠嗆的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.64,0:08:27.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,破忌者部隊在軍隊裡也算是冷板凳下下籤啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.78,0:08:29.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過有那個國王陛下在
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.08,0:08:32.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定會說「為了羅蘭德的未來給我死命幹活」什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.80,0:08:33.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不讓你們偷懶吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.24,0:08:36.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 陛下為了造福我國
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.00,0:08:38.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直鞠躬盡瘁
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.24,0:08:41.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能為那樣傑出的國王工作
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.58,0:08:43.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們很幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.63,0:08:44.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就編吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.17,0:08:47.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實你還有很多牢騷想發吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.73,0:08:49.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如「別把人當騾子使喚」啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.05,0:08:51.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「趕快加薪吧」什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.75,0:08:54.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「午睡時間每天給我24小時以上」之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.32,0:08:57.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是一整天都在睡了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.84,0:09:01.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然不能讓隊長嫁給這種人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.88,0:09:03.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？你說啥
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.02,0:09:05.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萊納
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.19,0:09:10.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蜜爾可 -蜜爾可隊長
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.84,0:09:12.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可得給我解釋清楚 萊納
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.95,0:09:16.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的私生子 私藏的老婆
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.43,0:09:17.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈爾法和盧納的情婦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.11,0:09:19.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有還有
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.51,0:09:20.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之一大堆
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.04,0:09:22.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾所求雷鳴
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.41,0:09:23.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,電光
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.40,0:09:25.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您冷靜一點 蜜爾可隊長
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.91,0:09:26.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隊長？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.89,0:09:30.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我站住
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.92,0:09:32.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然搞什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.86,0:09:35.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲莉絲
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.36,0:09:40.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,維尼特糰子店剛做好的丸子真是不同凡響啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.83,0:09:42.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,維尼特糰子店？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.06,0:09:44.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從哪兒弄來的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.69,0:09:46.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然是買來的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.49,0:09:48.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為這裡是羅蘭德國內啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.96,0:09:49.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.92,0:09:51.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,位於羅蘭德沿岸部
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.87,0:09:53.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我艾利斯家領地之一
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.90,0:09:55.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這你都看得出來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.50,0:09:57.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從這裡還能看到艾利斯家的府邸
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.94,0:09:59.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們沒發現嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.57,0:10:01.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下面怎麼可能看得到
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.92,0:10:02.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不慢著
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.10,0:10:04.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡已經是羅蘭德了對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.97,0:10:05.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.11,0:10:07.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.69,0:10:10.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就去找讓我們落到這步田地的席恩報仇吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.23,0:10:14.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 打倒他的那一天
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.28,0:10:15.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就自立為王
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.85,0:10:18.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將羅蘭德變成糰子帝國吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.30,0:10:23.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要變就變成糰子與午睡帝國吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.48,0:10:26.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼九一分成 也加上午睡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.11,0:10:31.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼才九一啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.58,0:10:32.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也罷走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.72,0:10:36.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢 慢著 萊納
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.41,0:10:43.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕不放任目中無人的虐待狂大王席恩橫行霸道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.50,0:10:44.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.19,0:10:53.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過去在歷史上
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.59,0:10:57.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曾有力量強大到足以統治世界的魔王
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.20,0:11:01.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者人稱惡魔 邪神的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.99,0:11:04.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幾度差點毀滅了世界
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.13,0:11:05.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.25,0:11:07.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每當這種時候
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.41,0:11:08.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所謂傳說中的勇者
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.17,0:11:11.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,力量凌駕魔王之上的戰士
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.15,0:11:13.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就會擊潰這些怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.74,0:11:16.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連足以毀滅世界的怪物都能打倒的勇者
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.11,0:11:20.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若是能找到其遺物
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.19,0:11:25.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了創造任何人都不再失去的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.57,0:11:29.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家歡笑著 只要睡午覺就好的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.42,0:11:34.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,荒誕無稽…嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.25,0:11:41.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開什麼玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.69,0:11:45.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣的話 我是為了什麼而當王
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.97,0:11:48.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了改變這瘋狂的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.26,0:11:50.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了改變一切
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.08,0:11:54.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了創造大家都能幸福歡笑度日的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.89,0:11:58.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是為此才當上國王的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.85,0:12:02.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然說已經無能為力了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.59,0:12:04.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.24,0:12:06.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕不讓它發生
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.12,0:12:12.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.83,0:12:16.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來打掃嗎 抱歉嚇到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.12,0:12:20.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝您
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.39,0:12:23.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 我的故鄉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.42,0:12:25.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為領主大人的暴政和苛稅
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.45,0:12:26.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直深受其苦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.23,0:12:28.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多虧了陛下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.02,0:12:31.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家才能過上好日子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.72,0:12:35.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能為陛下工作 感到十分幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.53,0:12:39.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.75,0:12:45.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就說那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.15,0:12:47.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就會做表面功夫
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.37,0:12:51.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以大家都上了他的當
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.03,0:12:54.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說什麼英雄王的把人捧上天
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.84,0:12:58.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實他就一目中無人的虐待狂大王
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.12,0:13:00.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天一定要下手
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.00,0:13:03.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把那張若無其事的笑臉虐到死
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.38,0:13:05.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 讓他變成我劍上的銹
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.36,0:13:08.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萊納真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.73,0:13:10.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎怎怎怎麼辦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.57,0:13:12.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然要暗殺陛下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.96,0:13:14.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就覺得他不是普通的破忌者
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.34,0:13:17.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到是企圖顛覆國家的大壞蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.39,0:13:19.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是暗殺國王
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.14,0:13:22.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使未遂也難逃死罪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.24,0:13:24.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一一一一定要阻止他
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.78,0:13:27.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在萊納罪上加罪之前
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.32,0:13:28.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心吧隊長
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.09,0:13:30.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暗殺阿斯塔爾陛下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.04,0:13:32.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他想都別想
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.25,0:13:37.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉赫
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.24,0:13:38.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,振作點
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.88,0:13:39.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.12,0:13:41.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了菲莉絲
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.99,0:13:44.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺好像有殺氣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.87,0:13:45.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是錯覺吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.78,0:13:50.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說 要怎麼做才能虐死席恩那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.31,0:13:51.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.67,0:13:53.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把他喜歡的什麼東西偷走
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.86,0:13:55.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「我 我的寶貝…」
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.99,0:13:57.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「不 不行了…吧嗒」
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.07,0:13:59.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.38,0:14:00.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不錯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.47,0:14:02.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 席恩的寶貝是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.47,0:14:04.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,團 糰子嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.13,0:14:06.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是你喜歡的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.06,0:14:11.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們幹嘛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.89,0:14:14.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克拉烏·柯洛姆
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.01,0:14:16.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還以為是誰呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.50,0:14:17.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是盧克嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.98,0:14:20.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是被分配到破忌者部隊去了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.18,0:14:22.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.44,0:14:24.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是熟人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.44,0:14:26.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前在軍隊認識
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.33,0:14:30.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒是您 不是去艾斯塔布爾出差了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.93,0:14:32.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本來是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.67,0:14:36.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過聽到傳聞說有人要暗殺席恩
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.64,0:14:38.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就回來調查了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.75,0:14:40.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.05,0:14:42.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那倆人的事已經…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.85,0:14:43.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那倆人？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.54,0:14:46.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.98,0:14:49.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 我肚子痛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.05,0:14:51.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 要上廁所
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.03,0:14:53.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可真不得了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.21,0:14:55.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛 好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.85,0:14:54.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蜜爾可隊長
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.66,0:14:55.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,廁所在那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.04,0:14:57.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來 快去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.20,0:15:03.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.79,0:15:05.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 怎麼就跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.00,0:15:07.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 沒關係吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.63,0:15:09.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說席恩陛下一切可好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.18,0:15:12.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是那麼工作上癮
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.70,0:15:14.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不偶爾放個假的話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.35,0:15:17.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下面的人會累趴下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.23,0:15:21.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萊納
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.52,0:15:23.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定要保護你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.28,0:15:26.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萊納
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.33,0:15:28.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萊納
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.79,0:15:29.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蜜爾可臥倒
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.80,0:15:31.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾所求雷鳴
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.07,0:15:33.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,電光
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.72,0:15:37.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.17,0:15:40.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,退下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.53,0:15:41.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲莉絲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.38,0:15:50.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.22,0:15:51.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萊 萊納
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.38,0:15:52.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.28,0:15:53.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也搞不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.97,0:15:55.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得有殺氣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.01,0:15:58.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是盯上席恩的刺客什麼的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.58,0:16:00.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當國王真夠嗆啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.72,0:16:02.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別的刺客？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.25,0:16:07.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 萊納果然沒打算暗殺陛下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.25,0:16:08.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 對了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.75,0:16:09.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.22,0:16:11.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放著他們不管的話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.80,0:16:13.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不就能借刀殺人了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.87,0:16:14.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.71,0:16:16.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲莉絲住手住手
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.49,0:16:18.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放著他們不理反而比較好哎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.86,0:16:21.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萊納…你這個人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.97,0:16:23.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾所求雷鳴
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.81,0:16:24.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,電光
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.42,0:16:28.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,電光電光電光電了個光
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.93,0:16:29.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.82,0:16:31.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.78,0:16:35.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了對抗加斯塔克
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.72,0:16:37.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會需要最大限度的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.45,0:16:39.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.05,0:16:41.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是要先掌握艾斯塔布爾嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.44,0:16:44.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使軍隊交給克拉烏
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.10,0:16:46.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貴族們還是得由我…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.93,0:17:08.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殺人啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.30,0:17:10.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早啊 萊納
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.40,0:17:11.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早你個頭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.17,0:17:14.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我鼻子都快斷了喂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.69,0:17:16.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是也想暗算我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.23,0:17:18.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然在門上搞這種小動作
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.15,0:17:20.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幾時回來的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.25,0:17:21.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今早
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.20,0:17:23.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後呢 怎麼在我床上
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.06,0:17:26.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一言難盡啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.63,0:17:27.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯對了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.09,0:17:31.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我啊 領悟了一條大真理
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.57,0:17:32.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真理？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.07,0:17:35.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前我漂浮在海上
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.62,0:17:36.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.78,0:17:38.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全看不到岸
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.07,0:17:41.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四周無邊無際 天空高廣遼闊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.20,0:17:45.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只聽得到海浪聲和海鳥的叫聲
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.66,0:17:48.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫名地引人思考
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.76,0:17:51.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的人生這樣下去沒問題嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.00,0:17:55.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼我非得每天這麼拚命呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.61,0:17:57.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 明白明白
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.31,0:17:58.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.51,0:18:00.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後呢 我發覺了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.96,0:18:02.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那傢伙 都怪那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.02,0:18:05.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切都是那個十惡不赦的羅蘭德帝國國王
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.45,0:18:08.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,席恩·阿斯塔爾的錯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.06,0:18:08.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.94,0:18:09.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打算來殺我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.99,0:18:10.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.72,0:18:11.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用字典？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.03,0:18:13.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用字典
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.15,0:18:17.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是你這幾個月四處奔波所領悟的真理？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.90,0:18:19.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很強吧這理
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.52,0:18:26.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,強啊 真是強
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.33,0:18:29.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過萊納
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.86,0:18:31.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也太心急了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.93,0:18:33.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暗殺國王可是重罪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.16,0:18:37.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且還是全國民所敬愛的英雄王
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.24,0:18:41.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗚哇 居然自稱英雄王
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.67,0:18:43.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前我就在想了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.64,0:18:46.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那自信到底是從哪兒冒出來的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.92,0:18:49.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我生來就是要當王的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.47,0:18:51.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說這話不害臊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.90,0:18:53.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事實如此沒辦法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.62,0:18:55.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這光芒就與眾不同啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.67,0:18:59.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼說 從純粹的心中孕育出的聖人君子之光
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.79,0:19:01.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.20,0:19:03.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總 總之先殺了你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.51,0:19:06.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後我就能為這個國家帶來和平
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.42,0:19:08.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不 我說萊納
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.11,0:19:15.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,席恩
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.89,0:19:16.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.27,0:19:21.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你累了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.53,0:19:24.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.92,0:19:27.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.03,0:19:34.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經沒事了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.57,0:19:36.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛剛躺了會兒
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.42,0:19:37.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才一瞬間哎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.86,0:19:40.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是我一天能睡50小時
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.92,0:19:44.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一天50小時？那可真是技術啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.81,0:19:46.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也能行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.45,0:19:48.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那試試把工作全丟下？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.62,0:19:49.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.15,0:19:51.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就不行
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.94,0:19:56.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十惡不赦的糰子之敵 覺悟吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.73,0:19:59.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萊納 你醒醒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.15,0:20:04.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,王 王遭了變態色情狂的毒手
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.18,0:20:05.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.77,0:20:07.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿斯塔爾陛下？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.25,0:20:10.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼萊納會和陛下…？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.19,0:20:12.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.91,0:20:14.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起萊納
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.37,0:20:15.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直沒發現
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.02,0:20:17.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,縱然世人會冷眼相待
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.88,0:20:18.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但祝你幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.43,0:20:21.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你幹嘛擅自接受了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.08,0:20:30.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後 為了創造任何人都不再失去的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.13,0:20:33.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那女孩 姬琺不再哭泣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.58,0:20:36.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塔伊爾 托尼 琺露不會死
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.52,0:20:39.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,席恩也不用再自尋煩惱的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.24,0:20:44.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家歡笑著 只要睡睡午覺就好的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.21,0:20:46.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 楔子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.60,0:20:50.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蜜爾可·卡拉德是萊納·琉特的楔子嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.23,0:20:53.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了不讓萊納·琉特從羅蘭德…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.46,0:20:58.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 從席恩·阿斯塔爾身邊離開
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.74,0:21:02.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是王的弱點
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.28,0:21:06.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對萊納·琉特離開自己感到恐懼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.72,0:21:10.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇者遺物
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.99,0:21:14.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由此不殺人而創造和平的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.12,0:21:16.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萊納·琉特所期望的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.82,0:21:20.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有死亡 沒有殺戮 沒有悲傷
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.16,0:21:26.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,理想的王 那是束縛席恩·阿斯塔爾的鎖鏈
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.28,0:21:29.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而這會毀滅陛下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.53,0:21:32.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回應所有期待的理想國王
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.52,0:21:37.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種幻想 會讓人…讓王崩潰
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.94,0:21:43.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萊納·琉特…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.66,0:21:46.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有必要除掉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.55,0:22:04.87,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}忘れてたあの日の面影が
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.43,0:22:10.75,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}空の向こう 微かに
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.78,0:22:18.75,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}心なら繋がっていたはず
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.55,0:22:26.59,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}震えた瞳は答えずに
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.77,0:22:29.66,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}どんなに信じても
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.90,0:22:33.22,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}どんなに伝えたくても
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.43,0:22:39.46,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}この声は届かない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.31,0:22:44.23,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}光のフィルメント
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.37,0:22:49.13,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}全てをこの体に刻み
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.66,0:22:54.34,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}歩き出す ここから
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.42,0:22:57.97,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}記憶のセグメント
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.12,0:23:03.44,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}今からまる運命の糸解き
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.71,0:23:07.16,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}強くなりたい
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.26,0:23:12.24,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}また出会えなら もっと
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.53,0:23:19.88,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}守れるように 君を
